#Flight.Distance

# Create a histogram
ggplot(data = data, aes(x = Flight.Distance)) +
  geom_histogram(binwidth = 100, fill = "skyblue", color ="darkblue") +
  labs(title = "Histogram of Flight.Distance", x = "Flight Distance", y = "Frequency") +
  theme_minimal()

#Box plot
ggplot(data = data, aes(y = Flight.Distance)) +
  geom_boxplot(fill = "lightblue", color = "black") +
  labs(title = "Box Plot of Flight.Distance", y = "Flight Distance") +
  theme(plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5))

#Density plot
ggplot(data = data, aes(x = Flight.Distance)) +
  geom_density(fill = "skyblue", color = "darkblue") +
  labs(title = "Density Plot of Flight.Distance", x = "Flight Distance") +
  theme_minimal()

#QQ Plot
qqnorm(data$Flight.Distance, main= "QQ - Plot for Flight Distance")
qqline(data$Flight.Distance, col="Blue")

outlierKD2(data, data$Flight.Distance, rm = TRUE,qqplt = TRUE)
